rvices.msc -> Windows Update<br>    改为\"禁用“<br><br>3) 定期到<a href=\"https://www.catalog.update.microsoft.com/Home.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">Microsoft Update Catalog</a> 找到并下载当月Rollup更新, 视需要安装。建议与最新rollup保持一到两个月的时间差。<br><br>4) 如果新安装的系统直接安装下载的msu补丁包弹出\"不适合当前操作系统\"的提示, 大概率需要安装针对Windows Upadate 的更新(更新的更新, 厉害吧<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">), 这时候让它自动跟新一阵子应该就会装上, 期间提防Windows易升出没。<br><br>建议使用LTSB版本, 如果是开发需要(官方表示<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-cn/visualstudio/productinfo/vs2017-system-requirements-vs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">LTSB上不能使用VS2017进行开发</a>)也尽量安装与LTSB同版本号的Win10, 目前是1607(10.0.14393 周年更新), 按照时间表今年会发布新的LTSB版本。<br><br>如果不是驱动、新协议不兼容等蛋疼的原因, 又一定要用Windows的话, 还是用Win7吧<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/55/255501.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1330205","time":"2018-3-22 10:22","userId":"kakinuma","userName":"事实是柿子 - ⭐️VIP3","userSign":"","message":"最后一句最有用<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/92/79290.jpg","floor":"#5-2","id":"1330213","time":"2018-3-22 10:32","userId":"continuer","userName":"Euphy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">柿子 - ⭐️VIP3</span> 说: 最后一句最有用</q></div>Win7还可以用2年。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/84/268422.jpg","floor":"#5-3","id":"1330255","time":"2018-3-22 13:21","userId":"alexio_yorbmapr","userName":"海盗丸子","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Euphy</span> 说: Win7还可以用2年。</q></div>用Windows系统的人没几个开自动更新的，所以巨硬是否提供维护，意义都不是很大，多数还是靠第三方软件来提供安全<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#5-4","id":"1330267","time":"2018-3-22 14:00","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","m